1
00:00:07,380 --> 00:00:09,466
On the first day
when the Shangguan Group went public,

2
00:00:09,466 --> 00:00:11,400
a serious
public opinion crisis occurred,

3
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:12,460
leading to a sharp decline
in stock prices.

4
00:00:12,460 --> 00:00:15,300
Protesting shareholders gathered
outside the group's headquarters,

5
00:00:15,300 --> 00:00:16,460
making a huge commotion.

6
00:00:16,460 --> 00:00:17,340
[Shangguan Group]
Repay the money!

7
00:00:17,380 --> 00:00:18,260
[Shangguan Group]
Repay the money!

8
00:00:18,340 --> 00:00:19,220
[Shangguan Group]
Repay the money!

9
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:20,420
Stop shouting! Quiet down!

10
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:21,380
Repay the money!

11
00:00:21,420 --> 00:00:21,900
Stop shouting!

12
00:00:21,900 --> 00:00:23,780
Shangguan Xiao
has already been brought down by us.

13
00:00:23,780 --> 00:00:25,420
Now go grab his daughter.

14
00:00:25,420 --> 00:00:26,740
We must eradicate
the root of the problem.

15
00:00:28,660 --> 00:00:29,220
She's there!

16
00:00:29,220 --> 00:00:29,860
Catch her!

17
00:00:30,220 --> 00:00:31,220
Shangguan Chuxia,

18
00:00:31,380 --> 00:00:32,540
your father sent me to pick you up.

19
00:00:32,980 --> 00:00:33,780
They might leave from here.

20
00:00:33,780 --> 00:00:34,540
Stay here, guard this place.

21
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:35,060
They are here.

22
00:00:39,020 --> 00:00:39,660
Run!

23
00:00:45,820 --> 00:00:47,700
[Hedi West Road]

24
00:00:47,820 --> 00:00:48,900
Chuxia.

25
00:00:49,460 --> 00:00:51,220
Take care of yourself.

26
00:00:51,666 --> 00:00:53,900
Dad won't be able to be
by your side from now on.

27
00:00:55,166 --> 00:00:56,500
Dad!

28
00:00:57,380 --> 00:00:58,700
From that day onwards,

29
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:00,180
I lost my memory,

30
00:01:00,300 --> 00:01:02,300
opening up a completely different life.

31
00:01:05,606 --> 00:01:08,050
[Life is Drama]
[Episode 1]

32
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:09,940
[15 years later]

33
00:01:09,940 --> 00:01:11,800
[Feng Dongdong's house]
Is everything all right

34
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:12,580
with Dongdong and my engagement?

35
00:01:12,620 --> 00:01:13,620
[Qiao Li]
Don't worry.

36
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:15,740
I adopted this girl.

37
00:01:15,860 --> 00:01:17,180
She has to obey me.

38
00:01:17,660 --> 00:01:18,860
That's good.

39
00:01:19,260 --> 00:01:20,260
I like her very much.

40
00:01:21,100 --> 00:01:21,900
Dongdong!

41
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,800
Dongdong!

42
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:24,140
What is it?

43
00:01:25,300 --> 00:01:26,700
I've been calling
for so long but you didn't respond.

44
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:27,660
Duh.

45
00:01:27,940 --> 00:01:29,820
The dog barked several times
early in the morning,

46
00:01:29,820 --> 00:01:31,140
so I thought it was the dog again.

47
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,380
Come here!

48
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:36,620
I have to go to work soon.

49
00:01:36,620 --> 00:01:37,820
I have no time to waste here.

50
00:01:38,460 --> 00:01:39,380
Let me tell you,

51
00:01:39,380 --> 00:01:40,020
today is

52
00:01:40,020 --> 00:01:41,900
the day of your engagement with Wang!

53
00:01:41,900 --> 00:01:43,100
Whether you are willing or not,
you have to.

54
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:51,633
Have you got any news
on the investigation I asked you about?

55
00:01:51,633 --> 00:01:54,066
Are you referring to the girl
who disappeared fifteen years ago?

56
00:01:54,366 --> 00:01:55,180
Yes.

57
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:56,100
I have some news.

58
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:58,580
After she disappeared, she was
adopted by her current foster mother.

59
00:01:58,580 --> 00:02:00,180
She is now working
as a housekeeper at a hotel.

60
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:01,460
I've already sent someone
to investigate.

61
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:02,380
It seems her name is Feng Dongdong.

62
00:02:03,140 --> 00:02:04,020
Don't go, Dongdong.

63
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:04,540
Let go of me.

64
00:02:04,540 --> 00:02:05,380
Let's not quarrel.

65
00:02:05,466 --> 00:02:07,180
We're going to be family soon.

66
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:07,780
Here.

67
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:08,620
Let's have a toast.

68
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:11,660
You're the elder,

69
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:13,180
how can you toast me?

70
00:02:13,540 --> 00:02:13,980
Here.

71
00:02:13,980 --> 00:02:15,140
I'll toast you.

72
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:17,460
You...

73
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:19,860
How do you educate your daughter?

74
00:02:19,860 --> 00:02:20,400
Hey!

75
00:02:20,620 --> 00:02:21,500
She has no manners at all!

76
00:02:22,380 --> 00:02:23,420
Stop right there!

77
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:24,833
Let me tell you,

78
00:02:25,140 --> 00:02:27,140
don't use your identity
as a foster mother to pressure me again.

79
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:28,580
Don't try to force me into marriage.

80
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:46,500
[Huamao Tower]

81
00:02:47,460 --> 00:02:48,300
Ah!

82
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:49,020
Hmm.

83
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:50,300
A wonderful life begins.

84
00:02:51,540 --> 00:02:52,100
Feng Dongdong.

85
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,020
What's wrong with you?

86
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,366
You're late for work again today.

87
00:02:54,366 --> 00:02:55,300
I'm sorry, Sir.

88
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:56,220
Where are you now?

89
00:02:56,220 --> 00:02:57,980
I'm already in room 5916.

90
00:02:58,380 --> 00:02:59,660
Have you cleaned the room?

91
00:02:59,660 --> 00:02:59,900
Oh,

92
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:00,660
I'll go now.

93
00:03:04,266 --> 00:03:05,860
Hasn't the guest arrived yet?

94
00:03:25,220 --> 00:03:25,940
Hello.

95
00:03:25,940 --> 00:03:27,533
Please clean room 5909.

96
00:03:27,533 --> 00:03:28,220
Thank you.

97
00:03:31,166 --> 00:03:33,260
Oh no, I've come to the wrong room.

98
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:34,020
What should I do?

99
00:03:34,020 --> 00:03:36,180
He wouldn't find out, right?

100
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:49,540
Dongdong.

101
00:03:50,020 --> 00:03:51,100
What's wrong with you?

102
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:52,220
You're not answering calls.

103
00:03:53,060 --> 00:03:54,180
I'm sorry.

104
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:54,900
It's mine.

105
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,600
You little brat.

106
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:03,580
Yun Tun.

107
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:05,500
I want to complain
about this hotel's housekeeper.

108
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:06,540
What's wrong, Mr. Yun?

109
00:04:06,660 --> 00:04:07,700
She actually sneaked into my room

110
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:08,620
[Yun Tun]
and hid in my blanket.

111
00:04:09,820 --> 00:04:10,500
Feng Dongdong!

112
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,220
You must marry Wang today!

113
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:13,740
Stop right there!

114
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:14,940
Where do you think you're going?

115
00:04:14,940 --> 00:04:15,420
Help!

116
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:16,233
Girl!

117
00:04:16,233 --> 00:04:17,220
Stop right there!

118
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:17,820
Help!

119
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:18,900
Help!

120
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:20,460
Stop right there!

121
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:22,260
Stop right there!

122
00:04:27,340 --> 00:04:28,020
That's her.

123
00:04:30,860 --> 00:04:31,460
Stop right there!

124
00:04:33,020 --> 00:04:34,980
Hey, stop!

125
00:04:35,780 --> 00:04:36,580
Dongdong.

126
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:38,300
Wang loves you a lot.

127
00:04:38,300 --> 00:04:39,580
Follow me.

128
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:40,260
Let's go home.

129
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:40,660
Hurry up.

130
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:42,060
Let go of me!

131
00:04:42,060 --> 00:04:42,780
Ah!

132
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:43,660
Hey!

133
00:04:43,660 --> 00:04:44,460
Oh!

134
00:04:45,580 --> 00:04:46,580
Quick, save her!

135
00:04:46,580 --> 00:04:47,580
I can't swim!

136
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:49,380
She's supposed to marry you!

137
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:10,860
[Life is Drama]
